                  "fill": "#5A4D42",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": 560,
                  "content": "The menu already proves range, from bacon-and-queso classics to vegan cashew-queso builds and truffle tots. This section frames Frankie’s as a brand people trust for both indulgence and consistency.",
